'''玛格丽特·费里尔'''（{{lang-en|Margaret Ferrier}}，{{bd|1960年|9月10日|catIdx=Ferrier, Margaret}}），[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]政治人物，在2015年至2017件年及2019起擔任[[拉瑟格倫和西哈密爾頓_(英國國會選區)|拉瑟格伦和西哈密尔顿]]區英國國會議員。她是[[苏格兰民族党|苏格兰民族党]]黨員，但自2020年10月1日起因為違返2019年新型冠狀病毒防疫守則而被暫停黨籍。

==生平==
===早年及政治生涯前===
费里尔生於1960年9月10日<ref>{{cite web |title=Margaret Ferrier |url=http://myparliament.info/Member/4386 |website=myparliament.info |publisher=MyParliament |access-date=11 August 2017 |archive-date=2016-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160524030924/http://myparliament.info/Member/4386 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在[[格拉斯哥|格拉斯哥]]{{link-en|國王公園 (格拉斯哥)|King's Park, Glasgow|國王公園}}長大<ref name=opens>{{cite news | title = Margaret Ferrier opens up to the Reformer on politics, independence and Westminster | url = http://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/news/local-news/rutherglens-new-mp-margaret-ferrier-5855903 | newspaper = Daily Record / Rutherglen Reformer | first = Douglas | last = Dickie | date = 15 June 2015 | accessdate = 11 August 2017 | archive-date = 2020-11-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201128155745/https://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/news/local-news/rutherglens-new-mp-margaret-ferrier-5855903 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。與家人在西班牙[[馬略卡島|馬略卡島]]生活兩年後，她在1972搬回蘇格蘭[[拉瑟格伦|拉瑟格伦]]，1990年搬至[[达恩利|达恩利]]，2000年起在[[坎巴斯兰|坎巴斯兰]]生活。2011年她加入[[苏格兰民族党|苏格兰民族党]]成為黨員<ref name=opens/>。

她在大學時修讀航運管理。在當選為下議院議員前，费里尔在马瑟韦尔一家製造建築公司擔任銷售主管<ref name="daily-record-2015-selection">{{cite news | title = SNP select Margaret Ferrier as candidate for Rutherglen and Hamilton West seat in the General Election | url = http://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/news/local-news/snp-select-margaret-ferrier-candidate-5106410 | newspaper = Daily Record / Rutherglen Reformer | first = William | last = Henshaw | date = 5 February 2015 | accessdate = 1 June 2015 | archive-date = 2020-10-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201009040100/https://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/news/local-news/snp-select-margaret-ferrier-candidate-5106410 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

===政治生涯===
在進入西敏寺前，她曾參選2013年[[南拉纳克郡|南拉纳克郡]]議會選舉，在南拉瑟格倫選區參選，但輸給[[苏格兰工党|苏格兰工党]]的{{link-en|格德·基伦|Ged Killen}}<ref name=SLC13>{{cite news |url=http://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/news/local-news/killen-wins-rutherglen-south-labour-2540587 |title=Killen wins Rutherglen South for Labour |first=Douglas |last=Dickie |newspaper=Daily Record / Rutherglen Reformer |publisher=Trinity Mirror |date=20 February 2013 |accessdate=13 June 2017 |archive-date=2020-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200615094455/https://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/news/local-news/killen-wins-rutherglen-south-labour-2540587 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[2015年英國大選|2015年英國大選]]中，她在[[拉瑟格倫和西哈密爾頓_(英國國會選區)|拉瑟格倫和西哈密爾頓]]選區參選並勝出<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/politics/constituencies/S14000056 |title=Election 2015: Rutherglen & Hamilton West |website=BBC News |accessdate=1 June 2015 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108110732/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/politics/constituencies/S14000056 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/news/local-news/rutherglen-hamilton-west-election-results-5658514 |title=Rutherglen and Hamilton West election results: SNP's Margaret Ferrier takes Labour hotspot with 52 per cent of the vote |first=Douglas |last=Dickie |work=Daily Record / [utherglen Reformer |publisher=Trinity Mirror |date=8 May 2015 |accessdate=8 May 2015 |archive-date=2020-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200615092724/https://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/news/local-news/rutherglen-hamilton-west-election-results-5658514 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，取得30,279票，共佔選區所有票的52%。[[2017年英國大選|2017年英國大選]]中，她的議席以265票之差丟給了格德·基伦<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/news/local-news/rutherglen-hamilton-west-election-results-5658514 |title=Labour gain first Scottish seat from SNP in election |first=Aiden |last=Kerr |publisher=STV Group |date=9 June 2017 |accessdate=9 June 2017 |archive-date=2020-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200615092724/https://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/news/local-news/rutherglen-hamilton-west-election-results-5658514 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/news/local-news/labour-takes-rutherglen-hamilton-west-10590345 |title=Labour takes Rutherglen and Hamilton West |first=Murray |last=Spooner |newspaper=aily Record / Rutherglen Reformer |publisher=Trinity Mirror |date=9 June 2017 |accessdate=9 June 2017 |archive-date=2018-06-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180625213746/https://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/news/local-news/labour-takes-rutherglen-hamilton-west-10590345 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而在[[2019年英國大選|2019年英國大選]]中，她以5,230票之差擊敗基伦奪回議席<ref name="BBC-S14000056">{{cite web |title=Rutherglen & Hamilton West parliamentary constituency - Election 2019 |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/politics/constituencies/S14000056 |website=BBC News |accessdate=1 October 2020 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108110732/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/politics/constituencies/S14000056 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

====2019新型冠狀病毒事件====
2020年9月26日，费里尔發現自己有[[2019新型冠狀病毒|2019新型冠狀病毒]]病徵後，便去進行病毒測試。同日她亦到訪了一家健身中心，美容中心和禮品店<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/news/scottish-news/snp-mp-margaret-ferrier-who-22783922|title=SNP MP Ferrier who has Covid visited beauty salon and gym on day she took test|first=Kirsty|last=Feerick|date=2 October 2020|work=Daily Record|accessdate=2020-10-05|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118055544/https://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/news/scottish-news/snp-mp-margaret-ferrier-who-22783922|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Police investigate Margaret Ferrier as MP defies calls to step down |url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2020/oct/02/margaret-ferrier-defies-westminster-clamour-mp-covid-scottish |website=The Guardian |accessdate=4 October 2020 |date=2 October 2020 |archive-date=2021-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116185642/https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2020/oct/02/margaret-ferrier-defies-westminster-clamour-mp-covid-scottish |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在等候結果期間，9月28日她乘火車到倫敦國會進行辯論<ref name=guardiancovid>{{Cite news |author1= Weaver, Matthew |author2= Brooks, Libby |title= SNP MP Margaret Ferrier suspended for taking train after positive Covid test |date= 1 October 2020 |url= https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/oct/01/snp-mp-margaret-ferrier-took-train-after-positive-covid-test |newspaper= [[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |access-date= 1 October 2020 |archive-date= 2021-02-14 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210214203301/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/oct/01/snp-mp-margaret-ferrier-took-train-after-positive-covid-test |dead-url= no }}</ref>，同日晚上她得到結果是呈陽性反應。29日她乘火車回蘇格蘭，並告訴[[黨鞭|黨鞭]]她的一名家庭成員不適<ref name=guardiancovid />。10月1日，她發表公告，對違反防疫守則道歉。此後她被暫停黨籍，並交回警方及國會標準局（Parliamentary standards authorities）處理<ref>{{cite web|title=SNP MP Margaret Ferrier suspended after knowingly travelling on 4 hour train journey with virus|url=https://www.heraldscotland.com/news/18763964.snp-mp-margaret-ferrier-suspended-knowingly-travelling-4-hour-train-journey-virus/|access-date=1 October 2020|website=The Herald|date=1 October 2020|archive-date=2020-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030140236/https://www.heraldscotland.com/news/18763964.snp-mp-margaret-ferrier-suspended-knowingly-travelling-4-hour-train-journey-virus/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10月2日，黨領袖及蘇格蘭首席部長[[妮古拉·斯特金|妮古拉·斯特金]]告訴她應該辭去議員一職<ref name="BBC-54383281">{{cite news |title=Sturgeon: Covid trip MP must 'do the right thing' |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-scotland-54383281 |accessdate=2 October 2020 |work=BBC News |date=2 October 2020 |archive-date=2021-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118094657/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-scotland-54383281 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[下議院議長_(英國)|下議院議長]][[林賽·霍伊爾|林賽·霍伊爾]]形容她的行為「不負責任」<ref>{{Cite news|date=2 October 2020|title=Commons speaker angry at 'reckless' Covid trip MP|work=BBC News|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-scotland-54383281|access-date=2 October 2020|archive-date=2020-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119003222/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-scotland-54383281|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

